# Formspree form ID for the "Book an Appointment" form.
# 1. Create a form at https://formspree.io and set its send-to email to sales@royalcrestgems.com
# 2. Copy the ID from the endpoint URL: https://formspree.io/f/<THIS_PART>
# 3. Copy this file to ".env.local" and paste the ID below, then rebuild.
#
# The live form ID (mrevvkrb) is already the built-in default in the code,
# so this only needs to be set if you want to point the form at a DIFFERENT form.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID=
